etics during the porosity evolution, and demonstrate the\napplicability of the developed model in predicting the linkage of densification\nfactor to the specific energy input during SLS.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Feb 2019 17:54:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Feb 2019 11:13:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-09"}
