 can be applied for the\nteleoperation of industrial/surgical robots independently or in coordination\nwith hands in the future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Feb 2019 05:51:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-14"}
