e. We conclude\nthat a mission to 1I/'Oumuamua is feasible, using existing and near-term\ntechnologies and there is sufficient time for developing such a mission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Feb 2019 14:49:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 May 2019 14:23:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
