acterize tear film dynamics in more detail compared to\nprevious methods based on high speed videokeratoscopy. It showed good\ncorrelation with manual assessment of tear film.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Feb 2019 14:52:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-15"}
